{"tid":900293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【早前傳入院】93歲利孝和夫人由利承武攙扶現身 左邊嘴角有傷口","createTime":"2018-11-13T06:25:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T07:15:43.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a184b509bca6d6fb235aec3849e209ac6039ae9d","tid":900293,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T06:25:29.000Z","msg":"現年93歲的利孝和夫人（陸雁群）最近傳出身體抱恙，有傳在養和醫院接受治療，日前其女兒利蘊珍接受《蘋果》查詢表示：「媽咪好好，無事呀！」<br />\n今日，利孝和夫人現身銅鑼灣「利園三期」開幕儀式，四代同堂包括96歲的利榮傑夫人、利蘊蓮、利蘊珍、利易海倫、利子厚及其他家族成員聚集一堂，慶祝利氏家族紥根銅鑼灣95年。<br />\n活動原定11時舉行，最後延遲，等利孝和夫人抵達才開始。利夫人約於11時半現身，化了妝，也戴了珠寶，不過今次不是穿招牌旗袍，而是淺黃色上衣配西褲，行動緩慢，由侄孫利承武和利家第四代利明德（Zachary）攙扶，毋須輪椅，但左邊嘴角貼了膠布。利家在活動前透過公關表示不受訪。<br />\n現場聚集了大批傳媒，利孝和夫人亦一直保持笑容，精神不俗，在台上還向記者揮手，又從女兒利蘊蓮指示下望鏡頭，利家四代同堂還一齊在台上大合照。利孝和夫人約逗留了二十分鐘左右，之後由家人陪同下由秘密通道離開。<br />\n利孝和是無綫創辦人之一及第一任董事會主席，1949年娶社交界名媛陸雁群，利孝和於1980年利因心臟病去世，由「六叔」邵逸夫繼任無綫電視主席。<br />\n多年來，利孝和夫人擔任無綫非執行董事，一直十分熱衷出席無綫大型活動，包括每年11月19日台慶，又或擔任大型活動頒獎嘉賓。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181113/large/1542082435_7b43.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181113%2Flarge%2F1542082435_7b43.jpg&h=1e3efcd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181113/large/1542082436_c02c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181113%2Flarge%2F1542082436_c02c.jpg&h=f04ee283&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181113/large/1542082436_a6c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181113%2Flarge%2F1542082436_a6c8.jpg&h=c85991a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181113/58907040\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181113%2F58907040&d=eBtG1dX1tajTQDz0aFHU8Gi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=35b0259d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181113%2F58907040&h=afcea5b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181113/58907040</a>"},{"pid":"8d7b0a7f300bb94eaa4e308f789c6844ae1bde3e","tid":900293,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T06:27:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6cb3e964ff84fd74d1d48bb98375f7991576788","tid":900293,"uid":12021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T06:31:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"caa6b5dca69b68362293570761dd40beea7d806a","tid":900293,"uid":73613,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T06:34:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d25223924c1b49d03ea10513b34f7cf74334c4a9","tid":900293,"uid":143211,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T06:36:50.000Z","msg":"我係利孝和   我係夫人"},{"pid":"cac6db17706ced76939d68a07b978af7b290ffc7","tid":900293,"uid":2772,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"caa6b5dca69b68362293570761dd40beea7d806a","tid":900293,"uid":73613,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T06:34:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T06:36:59.000Z","msg":"係 佢同佢老公既配合可以話係毫無破綻"},{"pid":"6ab840147657f93d9c53f502c67d1f98db24cb2b","tid":900293,"uid":62011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T06:40:54.000Z","msg":"都個頭近啦。"},{"pid":"a8d4eaa265db6df42bf8eb2371404a03856c7e40","tid":900293,"uid":196552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T06:43:45.000Z","msg":"而家先知利孝和夫人個真名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9146385dd4eba0ce238ff27fe9ff8d1997c4dd4","tid":900293,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8d4eaa265db6df42bf8eb237